20:07.000 --> 20:08.800
 Science doesn't prove anything.

20:08.800 --> 20:10.680
 It just reduces uncertainty.

20:10.680 --> 20:12.320
 Could the earth actually be flat?

20:13.960 --> 20:18.960
 Extremely unlikely, extremely unlikely.

