 But I still can't prove that I'm not living in a simulation,

20:59.360 --> 21:00.520
 that I'm not a brain in a vat,

21:00.520 --> 21:02.640
 that this isn't all an elaborate ruse

21:02.640 --> 21:04.600
 created by some technologically advanced

21:04.600 --> 21:06.520
 extraterrestrial civilization.

