 So if you just have a robot that not screams,

29:25.640 --> 29:28.440
 just like moans in pain if you kick it,

29:28.440 --> 29:30.920
 that immediately just puts it in a class

29:30.920 --> 29:35.280
 that we humans, it becomes, we anthropomorphize it.

